    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Development of this game is on hiatus. Release date is unknown at this time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Do You Like Sparklies?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raven Gold is a game founded on the concept of rewarding exploration. Explore handcrafted dungeons and find piles of hidden treasure</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042160/extras/screenshot7.PNG?t=1762102704\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve unique, challenging, handcrafted puzzles to find incredible treasure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042160/extras/Screenshot4-1.PNG?t=1762102704\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But it's not just a casual stroll in the park! Face off with hordes of enemies! Use your wits to take on powerful bosses that have been carefully programmed with unique skills and behaviours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042160/extras/Screenshot3-1.PNG?t=1762102704\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you've accrued some gold, decide what to do with it! Raven gold features a myriad of ways to spend your cash, from buying gear, to crafting, to buying key items that add to your experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042160/extras/Screenshot8-1.PNG?t=1762102704\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And if you're looking for an interesting story, there's one of those too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042160/extras/Screenshot2-1.PNG?t=1762102704\" /></span></p>",
